Package project1

Class EventOrganizer

java.lang.Object
project1.EventOrganizer
public class EventOrganizer extends Object
This class interprets user commands to interact with EventCalendar An instance of this class can process a single or multiple command lines. Processes command line inputs until Q is inputted.
Author:
Donald Yubeaton, Micheal Kassie
